The company, Alphacom has 30 years of history with over 50,000 employees and growing and revenue is growing at the rate of 18%. So, it's the good time to move 
all their resources on cloud.

They have banking services, so they can use Private cloud for extra security.
For healthcare they can use either private or public cloud.
For transport they can use public cloud.

Overall they can get a hybrid cloud for their available services.

The company can use Amazon's AWS, Microsoft's Aure, Rackspace's Openstack cloud for IaaS, Paas and SaaS.
